description: North Irving is kept pretty cool, thanks to Kona Ice and its mighty selection of flavors for the perfectly sweet icy treat, adored by adults and kids alike.Use the Flavorwave to create your own treat, it’ll surely be your new fave.There’s no better way to refresh yourself on a hot Texas day than with delicious tropical shaved ice, so surely have Kona Ice come your way.
name: Kona Ice of North Irving
